        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3 id="Build-a-gitee-repository"><a href="#Build-a-gitee-repository" class="headerlink" title="Build a gitee repository"></a>Build a gitee repository</h3><ul><li><p>clone my repositoryï¼š</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git <span class="built_in">clone</span> https://gitee.com/mathieulin/blog.git</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>download node and npm<br><a href="https://blog.csdn.net/weixin_46030002/article/details/126939600">guide</a></p></li><li><p>enter the repository and download npm package</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>create a gitee repository<br>Change _config.yml-deploy-repo to your own repository name<br>root is the same<br>Then in the repository, click on Gitee Pages under the service and turn on the mandatory use of HTTPS.</p></li></ul><h3 id="Get-started"><a href="#Get-started" class="headerlink" title="Get started"></a>Get started</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo clean</span><br><span class="line">hexo g</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">## local run</span></span><br><span class="line">hexo s</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">## deployment</span></span><br><span class="line">hexo d</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
      
